{"tid":94470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇全能嘅巴絲打知佢係乜黎","createTime":"2017-01-25T08:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T12:18:22.000Z","uid":66508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f231f00c9d6aa78f00f29d8e9a0294bdb23c1c","tid":94470,"uid":66508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02264FW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02264FW.jpg&h=32f323dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/No0s7Wr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNo0s7Wr.jpg&h=f79f3827&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/163802_183a2ef1ad1342814e9c393123b63e47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F163802_183a2ef1ad1342814e9c393123b63e47.jpg&h=dba93ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知呢隻係咩黎，<br />\n又係因咩而黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間屋最近多左好多好難頂 <br />\n打極都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係知佢向光，會俾野食嘅味引黎，<br />\n但好似唔咬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴絲打解答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想再見到佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0c491da960e5bcdc22fd7d30a3f2d3072a7c6d","tid":94470,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"小強d近親？<br />\nBtw最後張圖m巾黎架？咁多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47edf15ee2c7da66ab1bcdc54214a03b32f2fa1b","tid":94470,"uid":66508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小強d近親？<br />\nBtw最後張圖m巾黎架？咁多毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚細隻嫁咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只係我放大左<br />\n好似蚊滋仔咁<br />\n<br />\n係m巾黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去廁所嘅時候佢係身邊飛黎飛去<br />\n咁岩換緊m巾就一手痴落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c912a194c04aa14b608d720479b3a3f4c55d7034","tid":94470,"uid":4200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"應該係德國強，一個卵有幾十隻，rip"},{"pid":"2aee17d1610ff495e9534d97af04ffd5293394ab","tid":94470,"uid":66508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係德國強，一個卵有幾十隻，rip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻隻都曉飛嫁喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好細隻嫁喎，蚊滋咁嫁喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好嚇我，心血少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6136733cf8a3be03881780fa0566b808e742be","tid":94470,"uid":66508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以答到我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747de1188c80c8eaa35db4aef070a9c92883ded3","tid":94470,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"M巾同閪毛都出埋  邊夠你玩呀<br />\n娘娘收兵既手法層出不窮"},{"pid":"788c240edc1c1509c8a1ca4acfbeccbf16378ae1","tid":94470,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M巾同閪毛都出埋  邊夠你玩呀<br />\n娘娘收兵既手法層出不窮</blockquote><br />\n好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cd6a1fc5e3ec72dd2a072b4b8fa30d2c529892","tid":94470,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M巾同閪毛都出埋  邊夠你玩呀<br />\n娘娘收兵既手法層出不窮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n誇撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有啲閪水<br />\n實爆pm"},{"pid":"ad1c68f305effbfa251b3772e161d06eed8b6661","tid":94470,"uid":57875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"多毛蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab023d2965387dcea58f9a640605772b9d13e76","tid":94470,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71baa98db61a313d4185bb26e2ac08969730a77","tid":94470,"uid":66508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M巾同閪毛都出埋  邊夠你玩呀<br />\n娘娘收兵既手法層出不窮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係幾冇常識先會當做閪毛<br />\n你塊m巾痴底褲定痴閪啊？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5f1b463444d3ac36bdbfb799f5cd885d2d2958","tid":94470,"uid":66508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>M巾同閪毛都出埋  邊夠你玩呀<br />\n娘娘收兵既手法層出不窮</blockquote><br />\n好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n粒蟲核突啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471da37eea6ef33a619d97c5bf7ccc56329e09ac","tid":94470,"uid":66508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>M巾同閪毛都出埋  邊夠你玩呀<br />\n娘娘收兵既手法層出不窮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n誇撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要有啲閪水<br />\n實爆pm</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到黎嘅閪水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解我睇唔到"},{"pid":"0b592a7e1a84d8